00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:04,400
biryani recipe. I’ll also give you a couple

18
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:06,320
of tips on how to make it with chicken.

19
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:08,320
This involves a lot of steps, so make

20
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:10,479
